Add `MAINNET_URL=` to a .env file then run
`export RUST_BACKTRACE=full && export RUST_BACKTRACE=1 && forge test -w --mc TestFrxEthEthCurveLpDualOracle --mt testGetPrices`

@mattsse Im going to make the above repo private again, I found the (embarrassing) issue:
Its an overflow of the decimals field of assertApproxEqRelDecimal from forge-std.  
BAD:         assertApproxEqRelDecimal( _priceLow, _priceHigh, 1, 1e2);
GOOD:         assertApproxEqRelDecimal( _priceLow, _priceHigh, 1, 18);
